    description: "These are for fortifying a camp during the Encampment Raid scenario.  The defender may place up to three trap markers (per trap if you buy more than one) anywhere within their encampment.  Each marker is marked with either ‘trap' or ‘decoy,' on the underside [one trap to two decoys]. When a model touches the marker, flip it over.  If it says ‘decoy,' nothing happens.  If it says ‘trap,' then that model takes a Strength 4 hit with no armour save.",
